release_note: Minor updates
Minor updates.
This release introduces a new tab to help you track your journaling habit. Labeled frequency this calendar shows you every day you ve written a journal entry. Enjoy!
Minor updates and bug fixes.
Affirmations are now displayed from your Journals tab and can be sent to your phone s notification center. Please let us know what you think and enjoy!
Minor bug fixes
Introducing mood tracking! See how your mood changes over time. Any journal entries tagged with mood reaction emojis will be used to create charts that help you monitor your feelings.
Minor bug fixes.
Minor bug fixes and enhancements.
Check out our cool new app icon!
Customize the look and feel of your journals with stickers!
Customize the look and feel of journal bands!
Hotfix to make app work with iOS 16.
Minor bug fixes and enhancements.
We ve redesigned the home screen to show off your custom designed journal covers!
Behind the scenes fixes!
Minor bug fixes!

Now offering Seasons Premium! This is a paid subscription that allows you to create unlimited journals and unlocks all customization options. The free plan will continue to allow you to write as much as you d like in your first journal as well as join as many journals as you d like.
Minor fixes.
Minor improvements to the text editing experience.
Minor bug fixes.

In addition to writing in your journal you can now also post photos and make audio recordings! We ve also added the ability to pick and edit the date of your journal entries. Thanks for using Seasons Journaling!
Just a couple of minor bug fixes and optimizations.
A really small bug fix!
Happy New Year! This release includes a few minor fixes and enhancements. We also added a fresh batch of journal backgrounds to choose from. Hope you enjoy!

We ve added two more ways to customize your journals! Patterns and Frames are now available from the Seasons Shop allowing you to further customize the look and feel of your journal entries and notes. Thanks for using Seasons Journaling!
Customize your journals with one of four background images representing the seasons of the year! Thanks for using Seasons Journaling!

Additional celebrations are now available for purchase! Add confetti style animations to your journal entries for you or anyone else in your journal to enjoy. There are currently only a handful of new celebration types but we will be adding more soon!

We ve been hard at work! Hope you enjoy these new features : Thanks for using Seasons Journaling! Celebrations milestones now come equipped with a colorful and fun surprise! Keyword search a quick and easy way to jump back in time and look at previous journal entries. Face ID Passcode use the same Face ID and passcode for your phone to secure the app when you aren t using it. Re order journals drag and drop your journals and arrange them to your liking.
Journal with style! We added a few ways to style your reflections bold italic underline and strikethroughs . Thanks for using Seasons Journaling!

We are very excited to announce the addition of prompts to Seasons Journaling! Whether you are having trouble figuring out what to write about or looking to take your reflections to the next level we hope that prompts inspire and help you along your personal growth journey. As always please don t hesitate to let us know what you think! Thanks!
Minor bug fixes.
Several small enhancements and performance improvements. Thanks for using Seasons Journaling!
Bug fix for scheduling related to calendar access.

This update introduces two new features to help you stay motivated and committed to your journaling habit. Thanks for trying Seasons Journaling! Affirmations Receive daily affirmations written by you. Scheduling Set aside time in your day to write and reflect.
For those of you who are group journaling we have added an indicator to your journals with more than one person that will let you know when there are new entries to view. Hope you like it! Thanks!

This update follows our initial release with a handful of useful improvements. Enjoy and thank you for using Seasons Journaling! Save drafts never rush a reflection Edit journal details change the name description or category of your journals Email verification backup your data and sync across devices Fun and colorful design enhancements!
